  - m_Id: 18
    m_Localized: Window Repair
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 20
    m_Localized: A simple, rudimentary hammer. Using it will inhibit a random monster
      for ten seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 21
    m_Localized: A roll of good quality adhesive tape. It can be useful for repairing
      the cabin glass if it has cracked.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 22
    m_Localized: A fairly shiny and sturdy piece of metal. It will hold up for a
      while blocking the cabin door.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 24
    m_Localized: A rather elaborate and shiny hammer. It's so beautiful that instead
      of breaking things, it repairs them. Windows, for example.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 29
    m_Localized: Take a look.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 32
    m_Localized: It's a pleasure doing business with you.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 35
    m_Localized: Are you kidding me? If you don't have enough money, don't waste
      my time.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 38
    m_Localized: It doesn't look like you have enough space to store this, mate.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 41
    m_Localized: See ya 'round, pal.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 45
    m_Localized: This hammer is simple, but it might come in handy.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 46
    m_Localized: That tape is pretty strong, I'm sure you can fix something with
      it.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 47
    m_Localized: It's a piece of metal I found lying around, isn't it pretty?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 52
    m_Localized: I'll keep it
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 53
    m_Localized: What else you got?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 54
    m_Localized: Bullets
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 55
    m_Localized: Hammer
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 56
    m_Localized: Duct Tape
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 57
    m_Localized: Shiny Metal
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 58
    m_Localized: Engineer Hammer
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 59
    m_Localized: Silver Hammer
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 60
    m_Localized: Window Repair
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 26
    m_Localized: Good evening, friend. Need to stock up on supplies? I have some
      items that might be useful to you... provided you have enough currency, of
      course. What? You think the prices are inflated? Have you seen how things are
      out there? You won't find anyone else for a long distance. So take this offer
      or get lost!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 61
    m_Localized: Talk
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 62
    m_Localized: Leave
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 51
    m_Localized: I'm not interested
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 63
    m_Localized: Use
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 64
    m_Localized: Inspect
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 65
    m_Localized: Combine
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 66
    m_Localized: Toss
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 19
    m_Localized: A handful of lead bullets. With their use, any monsters found on
      the tracks will disappear instantly.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 23
    m_Localized: A professional-looking hammer. When used, a random monster will
      not approach for at least thirty seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 25
    m_Localized: A window repair kit. Use it on one window to repair it completely.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73
    m_Localized: A small pile of silver bullets. When used, any monsters on the tracks
      will disappear immediately and won't approach for at least fifteen seconds.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 74
    m_Localized: Silver Bullets
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75
    m_Localized: Can't be used
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76
    m_Localized: Can't be combined
    m_Metadata:
